MBclient version 1.50
=====================

Modbus is a standard serial communication protocol used to interconnect
industrial PLC (and a lot of other things). This module gives you access to
TCP and RTU version of this protocol, through the MBclient object.

See /docs for samples and full API documentation.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   sudo make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires no other module or librarie.

